name: ISINValidator_validateTest
description: Unit tests for the ISINValidator validate method with and without country code checks.

test_cases.name: testValidateWithCountryCheckValid
test_cases.description: Tests the validate method of ISINValidator with a valid ISIN and country code check enabled.

test_cases.name: testValidateWithCountryCheckInvalidCountryCode
test_cases.description: Tests the validate method of ISINValidator with an invalid country code and country code check enabled.

test_cases.name: testValidateWithoutCountryCheckValid
test_cases.description: Tests the validate method of ISINValidator with a valid ISIN and country code check disabled.

test_cases.name: testValidateWithoutCountryCheckInvalid
test_cases.description: Tests the validate method of ISINValidator with an invalid ISIN and country code check disabled.
